00:44:32.021 --> 00:44:34.559 line:93%
<i>Aku dikurung di sini sepanjang
malam, tapi kau membebaskan aku.</i>

00:44:34.559 --> 00:44:36.295 line:93%
<i>Aku tidak punya alasan 
untuk mendengarkanmu.</i>

00:44:36.766 --> 00:44:38.105 line:93%
<i>Hei, Kang Shin Woo!</i>

00:44:38.105 --> 00:44:39.786 line:93%
<i>Jangan pergi berkeliling
mengatakannya kepada orang lain.</i>

00:44:39.786 --> 00:44:41.572 line:93%
<i>Pada siapa lagi aku harus 
