00:44:48.795 --> 00:44:50.222 line:93%
<i>Kau menyukai Han Ji Soo, kan?</i>

00:44:50.222 --> 00:44:53.626 line:93%
<i>Yang merokok di kamar mandi
dan menyalakan api itu aku.</i>

00:44:53.626 --> 00:44:54.626 line:93%
